_sText:
This is a map which i created for an event within the PlagueFest community, where we had to make a map within 1024^3 units ONLY. So it didn't take too long to create at all.

This map includes these features:

  • 64 spawns
  • Cubemaps
  • HDR

FIX VERSION (NEW):

  • Balanced prop mass
  • Fixed a window being too narrow
  • Added some friendly little creatures across the map
  • Fixed/removed an unfair spot

Do not edit and/or reupload this map, although feel free to decompile it for learning purposes. Thanks!
